quran[11{c,v,t}:
7,1,"a, l-, m, s"
7,2,"yeh aik kitaab hai jo tumhari taraf nazil ki gayi hai, pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tumahray dil mein is se koi jhijak nah ho is ke utaarnay ki gharz yeh hai ke tum is ke zaryay se (munkareenko ) daraoo aur imaan laane walay logon ko yaad dehani ho"
7,3,"logo, jo kuch tumahray rab ki taraf se tum par nazil kya gaya hai uss ki pairwi karo aur apne rab ko chore kar dosray srprston ki pairwi nah karo magar tum nasiyaat kam hi mantay ho"
7,4,"kitni hi bastiyan hain jinhein hum ne halaak kar diya unn par hamara azaab achanak raat ke waqt toot para, ya din d_harhe aisay waqt aaya jab woh aaraam kar rahay thay"
7,5,aur jab hamara azaab unn par aa gaya to un ki zabaan par iss ke siwa koi sada nah thi ke waqai hum zalim thay
7,6,"pas yeh zaroor ho kar rehna hai ke hum unn logon se baz purse karen, jin ki taraf hum ne paighambar beje hain aur payghambaroon se bhi poucheen ( ke onhon ne pegham rasani ka farz kahan taq injaam diya aur inhen is ka kya jawab mila )"
7,7,"phir hum khud poor y ilm ke sath sarguzisht un ke agay paish kar den ge, aakhir hum kahin gayab to nahi thay"
7,8,aur wazan is roz ain haq hoga jin ke plrhe bhaari hon ge wohi Falah payen ge
7,9,aur jin ke plrhe halkay rahen ge wohi apne aap ko khasaray mein mubtala karne walay hon ge kyunkay woh hamari ayaat ke sath zalimana bartao karte rahay thay
7,10,"hum ne tumhen zameen mein ikhtiyarat ke sath basaayaa aur tumahray liye yahan samaan zeist faraham kya, magar tum log kam hi shukar guzaar hotay ho"
7,11,"hum ne tumhari takhleeq ki ibtida ki, phir tumhari soorat banai, phir firshton se kaha aadam ko sajda karo is hukum par sab ne sajda kya magar iblees sajda karne walon mein shaamil nah howa"
